data.description:
Beautiful updated 4 level family home in desirable Valley Hills!  Over 2400 sq. ft total.  This home has something for everyone in the family! 
   The furnished luxury master suite includes cathedral ceilings, bamboo floors, heated bathroom tile, wet bar, french doors that lead to a private balcony, a cedar lined walk in closet, & many more features. 
 The kitchen has been remodeled and features new hardwood floors,  a new convection gas stove and dishwasher, open bar area to living area that could also be used as a dining area!  The large walk out daylight basement has a completely remodeled bathroom and lots of room for the kids.  
    This home also has fresh paint inside & out, a new boiler, two covered redwood decks, a patio, mature landscaping, heated detached workshop with loft storage,  beautiful custom windows, large driveway, & many more features! 
    This wonderful family home exudes owner pride!
data.whatILove:
This home is in excellent condition & ready to move in to today!  The owners have lived here 23 years & raised their family in this wonderful neighborhood! 
     It’s also conveniently located just minutes away from west side shopping, entertainment, schools, medical offices, and restaurants, yet it is on a quiet street!
